@node HISTORY "History"


    @{"  " link  } 1.2 (16.12.97)

        @{" " link  } Fixed a small bug which would cause things like "CD0:"
           not to be properly deassigned.


    @{"  " link  } 1.1 (10.9.97)

        @{" " link  } Fixed a very dangerous bug caused by different treatment
           of .info files in DOS. If .info file was passed as argument
           to this script, it would eventually become the current directory!
           So it was very dangerous if someone used KILL option and selected
           icon file for deletion.


    @{"  " link  } 1.0 (21.8.97)

        @{" " link  } Initial version (you don't say :))

@endnode
